lead_paragraph: Hungary's Katinka Hosszu ended her long wait for Olympic victory and Australia captured two gold medals in an exhilarating first day of swimming competition that saw three world records smashed in Rio on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Swimming: Golden Start for Australia on Day of Records
